item.description:
Please join us on Sunday, November 23rd from 3-4:30pm for some small doggie fun!

As always, the health and saftey of our canine friends is our TOP priority! When dogs play together, it is very important that each dog is current on all of their vaccinations. These vaccinations include: DHLPP, Bordatella (canine cough) and Rabies. Please ensure that your dog is healthy and current on vaccinations prior to attending the meetup. If you have questions about this, please do not hesitate to let me know.
